    <item>
      <title>泰国内阁批准发放 44 亿美元现金以刺激经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/thai-cabinet-approves-4-4-billion-cash-handout-to-spur-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁批准了一项总额为 1456 亿泰铢（44 亿美元）的现金发放计划，该计划将使数百万穷人受益，并有助于刺激东南亚第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/thai-cabinet-approves-4-4-billion-cash-handout-to-spur-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 06:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟呼吁发行联合债券以弥补防空差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-urged-to-bolster-its-air-defense-gaps-by-issuing-joint-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁塞尔智库布鲁盖尔的最新报告称，欧盟应该考虑发行联合债券，为重大防空投资提供资金，以更好地保护其领空免受俄罗斯可能的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-urged-to-bolster-its-air-defense-gaps-by-issuing-joint-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默吸引投资者的计划取决于泰晤士水务公司的修复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/thames-water-crisis-hits-labour-s-hopes-for-foreign-infrastructure-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府将经济增长的希望寄托在从绿色能源到住房等各个领域的私人投资上。但泰晤士河事件让投资者大吃一惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/thames-water-crisis-hits-labour-s-hopes-for-foreign-infrastructure-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威克朗下跌，石油之都斯塔万格受压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-17/norway-krone-slide-leaves-oil-rich-stavanger-feeling-squeeze-nok-usd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2022 年以来，挪威克朗兑欧元已贬值约五分之一。这让这个世界上最富有、最昂贵的国家之一感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-17/norway-krone-slide-leaves-oil-rich-stavanger-feeling-squeeze-nok-usd</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称英国预算计划不会损害经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/starmer-says-he-won-t-hurt-economic-growth-with-uk-budget-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他将在政府即将出台的预算中优先考虑经济增长，尽管商界担心即将出台的增税和削减开支计划可能会阻碍英国经济发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/starmer-says-he-won-t-hurt-economic-growth-with-uk-budget-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹尼总理称，ISIS 失败意味着伊拉克不再需要美军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/isis-defeat-means-us-troops-no-longer-needed-in-iraq-says-pm-al-sudani</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克总理表示，由于美军已基本成功消灭伊斯兰国，伊拉克不再需要美军，他计划很快宣布撤军时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/isis-defeat-means-us-troops-no-longer-needed-in-iraq-says-pm-al-sudani</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
